Package: Logan mutation rate calculator
Type: Package
Title: Logan search result to Logan index bridge for mutation rate calculation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Arootin", "Gharibian", email = "arootin.gharibian@vsb.cz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimate, for each K-mer, how observed sequence variation deviates 
from published expectations by comparing measured diversity (π, θ) to expected
values derived from mutation rates and population parameters.
Depends: R (>= 4.4)
Imports:
